<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu hehpih mak, zahngaihna,
 A lungsiet na la'n sai tiu;
 Van gam In vak leh nuom achun,
 Umna ei siem sak ina.

[V2]
 Van gam nuom I tun tieng leh,
 Kipah, nawpna ni ahi na ding e;
 Lal Isu I muh tieng,
 Zawhna chuh pakchan lasa'i tiu.

[V3]
 2. Van gam zuona I chieh lai un,
 Meipi hung zing sek ina;
 Mahleh I zinnau a tawp tieng,
 Thim leh dahum bei tana.

[V4]
 3. Thutak, ginum in um hitiu,
 Nicheng a Lal na semin;
 Lopina muna I muh tieng,
 Sepgim man ei din tana.

[V5]
 4. I maua kipahman delh in,
 A hawihna mu pai tai tiu;
 Suongmantam kawt kihawng intin,
 Sana tuolah leng tai tiu.</lyrics>
<title>WHEN WE ALL GET TO HEAVEN</title>
</song>